Refined metals are purified forms of metal often used in higher-tier electronics due to their tendency to be able to withstand higher temperatures when they are made into wires. Other benefits include the increased decor value for some metals which can greatly improve the well-being of a colony.\n\nMetal ore can be refined in either the <link=\"ROCKCRUSHER\">Rock Crusher</link> or the <link=\"METALREFINERY\">Metal Refinery</link>.